snippet.title: Jim Connor 59
snippet.description:
Hi guys i have added my first story today The Elephant ride 
Please check it out leave comments ok
I will add other
tails and adventures.
From my life in the Royal Navy.
Traveling round the world.
Places and people i meet along the way.
India.
Diving under the sea.
Tagging a pyramid
Climbing in the Himalayas.
I have hundreds of traveler story's which i will share here on my channel.
So people please like and subscribe 
Leave comments 
I am dyslexic so writing stories down is very difficult i have always been good a telling a story. I think traveling helped.
I have been in two wars and survived.
So now i would like to share some of my experiences with you all hope you like them. If they don't work for you please let me know how i can make them more visual for you.
I will start with just me sitting by my phone chatting to you all and see how we go ok    
That's all for now love n peace 
Jimmy x
jimconnor59
/c/@youtube.com
